    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0884a21"/><head><date from-iso="0936-12-05" key="j20632662067017" to-iso="0947-03-14">晉</date>五臺山真容院<persName key="A013779">光嗣</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0884a22"/><persName key="A013779">釋光嗣</persName>，姓李氏，<placeName key="PL000000006042">太原文水</placeName>人也。沖幼孤靜，罕<lb
ed="T" n="0884a23"/>雜童稚。信尚臺山，乃為<placeName key="PL000000005387">真容院</placeName><persName key="A013780">浩威</persName>之高<lb
ed="T" n="0884a24"/>足也。納戒後，器宇穹隆，<anchor xml:id="beg0884001"/>㥽<anchor xml:id="end0884001"/>繫包桑，出求禪<lb
ed="T" n="0884a25"/>法，歷于年稔。內外之學優長，口海崩騰，良<lb
ed="T" n="0884a26"/>難抗敵。由是決意越重湖，登<placeName key="PL000000017104">閩</placeName>嶺，盛談<lb
ed="T" n="0884a27"/><persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>世界，聞者竦動。<persName key="A003732">忠懿王王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>大施香茗，<lb
ed="T" n="0884a28"/>遣使送山寺焉。<date key="j20546012054924" notAfter-iso="0914-02-02" notBefore-iso="0913-03-16">癸酉歲</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000008355">兩浙</placeName>，謁<persName key="A003552">武肅王<lb
ed="T" n="0884a29"/>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>厚禮遲之，施<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>聖眾供物香茶并鉢<pb ed="T" n="0884b" xml:id="T50.2061.0884b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0884b01"/>盂一萬。副應<placeName key="PL000000008355">吳越</placeName>諸州牧宰，皆刻俸入緣。<lb
ed="T" n="0884b02"/>仍泛海至<placeName key="PL000000003047">滄州</placeName>，運物入山。時<persName key="A009435">降龍大師</persName>者<lb
ed="T" n="0884b03"/>率領彈壓，緇伍畏焉，為其分散諸寺蘭若，<lb
ed="T" n="0884b04"/>眾寡均等。時徒侶堅請<persName key="A013779">嗣</persName>主院，宣補僧官<lb
ed="T" n="0884b05"/>轄諸<placeName key="PL000000005250">臺</placeName>寺院，命曰都綱，師號<persName key="A013779">超化</persName>，居于僧<lb
ed="T" n="0884b06"/>上，若鯤鳳之領鱗羽焉。十五年間，興建梵<lb
ed="T" n="0884b07"/>宇，齋飼僧尼，不勝紀極。以<date key="j20632662063340" notAfter-iso="0937-02-17" notBefore-iso="0936-12-05">天福元年</date>遘<lb
ed="T" n="0884b08"/>疾，至<date key="j20631982063198" when-iso="0936-09-28">九月五日</date><!--天福元年並無九月五日,應為清泰三年九月五日-->遷滅。門人起塔，藏其靈<lb
ed="T" n="0884b09"/>骨舍利，至今存焉。</p>
